// uniNN.uniL — UniLang Neural Network Model
// A complete, original neural network architecture built from scratch
// Designed as UniLang's flagship publishable model
//
// Model: UniNN (UniLang Neural Network)
// Architecture: Multi-head feed-forward with gated residual connections
//
